<section xml:id="ref.sites.web">
<title>Web Services</title>

<para>
Orc sites may provide access to Web services. 
A set of sites in the standard library provides facilities for accessing REST-based web services;
 support for SOAP-based services will be available in a future release. 
Sites which make direct GET and POST requests via HTTP are also available in the library. 
These sites return a single string, which may be used directly or parsed as XML input or JSON input by other library sites. 
</para>

